---
title: Island Bay Corn Fritters with Wedges, Pineapple Salsa & Mango Mayo
description: Take one part crunchy corn fritters, one part tangy salsa, and a whole lot of tropical island flair to create a delicious weeknight meal everyone will love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-island-bay-corn-fritters-a0094c72.jpg
